on set in the context of a hierarchical scenario for\nstructure formation. The models predict a scatter in the luminosities of the\nBCGs that is somewhat larger than the observed one, but that depends on the\ncriterion used to select the model clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jan 1998 13:07:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-30"}
